name: OBRJKT Rio de Janeiro #001
description: Face of the Christ the Redeemer, photographed from the arm of the monument, located on the Morro do Corcovado, in the city of Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. In the background, the Sugarloaf Mountain and the Guanabara Bay. Special item for #oBRjkt, a movement created to celebrate the potential of Brazilian NFTs that will take place on June 11, 12 and 13, 2021. | www.alexandremacieira.com.br
